🎨 DESIGN DOCUMENT

Product: ArthaPath Nepal
Version: 1.0
Type: UI/UX & Design System Specification
Mode: Light + Dark Toggleable
Design Inspiration: Modern Fintech Dashboard (data-centric, clean, high-contrast, card-based UI)

1. Design Principles

Clarity over decoration.

Data visibility first.

High contrast for financial numbers.

Minimal cognitive overload.

Trust-focused visual tone.

Dark mode default (finance users prefer dashboards at night).

Light mode must feel equally intentional (not inverted lazily).

2. Layout System
2.1 Grid

Max width: 1440px

Centered layout

8px spacing system

24px outer margin

16px default internal padding

24px section spacing

2.2 Page Structure
Desktop Layout
------------------------------------------------
Header
------------------------------------------------
Sidebar | Main Content Area
        | 
        | Cards / Charts / Panels
------------------------------------------------
Footer
------------------------------------------------
Mobile Layout
Header
Main Content
Bottom Navigation

Sidebar collapses into hamburger menu under 768px.

