Slightly increased letter spacing

5. Core Components
5.1 Header

Elements:

Logo (left)

Navigation: Dashboard | Explore | Simulator | Education

Theme toggle (icon switch)

Notification icon

Profile dropdown

Sticky at top.
Height: 72px.

5.2 Sidebar (Desktop)

Width: 240px

Menu Items:

Dashboard

Investment Plan

Opportunities

Simulator

Education

Settings

Active item:

Accent left border

Slight background highlight

Collapsible on tablet/mobile.

5.3 Card Component

Base Style:

Border radius: 16px

Padding: 20px

Shadow (light): subtle 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)

Shadow (dark): subtle glow 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)

Variants:

Summary Card

Metric Card

Chart Card

Allocation Card

5.4 Metric Card

Contains:

Label

Large numeric value

% change indicator (green/red)

Small contextual text

Example:
"Projected Value (5 Years)"
NPR 485,000
+32% Expected Growth

5.5 Investment Allocation Card

Contains:

Pie chart (percentage distribution)

Allocation breakdown list

Capital amount per category

Risk label badge

Badge styles:

Low Risk: green background

Medium Risk: orange

High Risk: red

5.6 Chart Components

Charts required:

Line Chart – Projection Growth

Pie Chart – Allocation

Bar Chart – Scenario Comparison

Chart Requirements:

Dark mode compatible colors

Axis labels clear

Tooltips enabled

Smooth animation on load

No heavy gradients

5.7 Input Components

Input Fields:

Amount (numeric)

Monthly contribution (numeric)

Duration (dropdown)

Risk slider (Low–Medium–High)

Input Design:

12px radius

Clear focus outline (accent color)

Inline validation errors in red

5.8 Buttons

Primary Button:

Accent background

White text

Hover lighten 5%

Secondary Button:

Transparent

Accent border

Accent text

Danger Button:

Red background

White text

6. Theme Toggle System

Theme stored in:

LocalStorage

Default: Dark

Implementation rule:

Use CSS variables or design tokens.

No manual class overrides per component.

Entire app must switch via theme provider.

